WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.447 --> 00:00:03.429
A challenge faced by hospitals around the world

2
00:00:03.429 --> 00:00:05.941
is reducing waste and improving efficiency

3
00:00:05.941 --> 00:00:07.925
in supply chain healthcare.

4
00:00:07.925 --> 00:00:11.460
Much of the hospital expenses, up to 80%,

5
00:00:11.460 --> 00:00:12.853
can be tied up in activities

6
00:00:12.853 --> 00:00:15.121
related to patient centered care.

7
00:00:15.121 --> 00:00:17.292
If hospitals can improve their performance

8
00:00:17.292 --> 00:00:19.481
in patient centered care activities

9
00:00:19.481 --> 00:00:21.828
such as managing supplies and equipment,

10
00:00:21.828 --> 00:00:24.365
managing facilities, and managing labor,

11
00:00:24.365 --> 00:00:26.867
it can lead to considerably cost savings.

